653	/// Case 3 — retriever invest + access-probe. The access-probe doubles as the
654	/// IAM-propagation gate: the invest tabtarget is responsible for waiting on
655	/// propagation before exiting (or the probe iterates internally). No separate
656	/// propagation-wait case.
657	fn rbtdrk_retriever_invest(dir: &Path) -> rbtdre_Verdict {
